Other shit you should know about the OS:

- terminal font is: "hack"
- System font: System San Francisco Display Regular
- Remember to use --no-startup-id on all exec'd things in your i3 config
- For the xorg.conf, change the graphics driver name
- Packages to install:
	- i3blocks
	- rofi
	- screenfetch
	- i3-gaps
	- URxvt
	- GTK arc-theme
	- Firefox arc-theme
	- Paper icon theme (put in .icons folder)
	- lxappearance
	- vim
	- git
	- lemonbar (ttf fork version)
	
